cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR 

The paper proposes a novel approach for goal-oriented reinforcement learning using a convolutional neural network. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses navigation and exploration in RL environments, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.GR (Graphics).
